Instalación MySql

1. Descargar base de datos 
	http://dev.mysql.com/downloads/file.php?id=458258
	manual -(https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O4xXzTIcnDE)

2. Descomprimir el zip
3. Crear la variable de entorno
	MYSQL_HOME
	path - %MYSQL_HOME%/bin
	
4. Abri cmd como administrador
	4.1 ir a la ruta %MYSQL_HOME%/bin
	4.2 ejecutar mysqld --install
	4.3 mysql -u root -p
	use mysql;
	update mysql.user set password = password('root') where user = 'root';
	delete from user where user = '';
	
	create database mycityviewdb default character set utf8 default collate utf8_general_ci;
	create user 'app_user'@'localhost' identified by 'mypass';
	grant all on mycityviewdb.* to 'app_user'@'localhost';
	flush privileges;
	quit
	
	mysql -u app_user -p
	use mycityviewdb;
	
MySql installer (Instalar requisitos para workbench)
	https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/file.php?id=458482
	
5. MySql workbench (el instalador)
	http://dev.mysql.com/downloads/file.php?id=457780
	



conector eclipse - (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FtCI3PIY4oE)


